               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18390617-name-803" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18390617-name-803" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18390617-name-803" type="surname" value="ARMSTRONG"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18390617-name-803" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN ARMSTRONG</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a bookseller, in partnership with Alexander Blake, in Wellington-street, Strand. The prisoner was my errand-boy—I have lost a pencil-case—I saw it safe a day or two before—this is it—here is the name of the maker on it—it belongs to the firm.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18390617-name-804" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18390617-name-804" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18390617-name-804" type="surname" value="SEARLE"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18390617-name-804" type="given" value="GEORGE"></interp>GEORGE SEARLE</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable F</hi> 143.) About eleven o'clock in the forenoon, on the 10th of June, I was in Bow-street on duty—I saw the prisoner with a pencil-case in his hand, looking at it—I asked where he got it—he said he bought it of a boy for 3<hi rend="italic">d</hi>., and he should know the boy—I took him into custody—he told me where he was living—I took the pencil-case there, and they owned it—he afterwards said, first, that he picked it up in the shop, and after, that he opened the cases, took one out, and put it in his pocket.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I was dusting my master's desk down, and saw the pencil-case—I took it to look at, some one came in, and I forgot it—I was going along Bow-street, and put my hand into my pocket and found it—I was looking at it, and was taken.</p>
               <p>
